    <description>20% 5-ALA Levulan Kerastick will be crushed and prepared for application after shaking for at least 3 minutes. Topical 5-ALA will be applied liberally on skin with extra pressure on lesions.Skin will be exposed to Candela V-beam Pulsed Dye Laser (595 nm).</description>
    <arm_group_label>2</arm_group_label>
